column2: Enter your 1 Rep Maxes in the yellow boxes, your initial training maxes will be calculated at 90% of your true max.
Each wave, your training max will increase according to the rules below
In some circumstances you may have to manually update your TMs, check the rules below
Assistance work is done with bodybuilding sets/reps, and can be changed to fit your needs
For OHP, just increase 5lb per wave unless you feel RPE 10 at any point, then drop 10% next wave
How much you will increase your TM each wave is based on how you perform in the 1+ sets
Your new TM will be calculated as halfway between your old TM and your predicted 1RM based on the AMRAP
If you fail to make even a single rep or only make one two weeks in a row, manually drop the TM 10-20% next wave

column7: Each wave, increase the weight if the number of reps
exceeded 5 in the last set of the last week
